title: UpgradeStatsWhenPossible
---
Meta Terminal: Which vital would you like to upgrade?
<<declare $currentLv = 0>>
<<declare $newLv = 0>>
-> Health
    <<set $currentLv = get_current_health_upgrade_level()>>
    Meta Terminal: Are you sure?
        -> Yes
            Meta Terminal: Making health upgrade now.
            <<trigger_stat_upgrade 0>>
            <<wait 2>>
            <<set $newLv = get_current_health_upgrade_level()>>
            <<if $newLv > $currentLv>>
                Meta Terminal: Success
            <<else>> 
                Meta Terminal: Failure
            <<endif>>
            <<jump TerminalGeneralDirectory>>
-> Stamina
    <<set $currentLv = get_current_stamina_upgrade_level()>>
    Meta Terminal: Are you sure?
        -> Yes
            Meta Terminal: Commencing stamina upgrade now.
            <<trigger_stat_upgrade 1>>
            <<wait 2>>
            <<set $newLv = get_current_stamina_upgrade_level()>>
            <<if $newLv > $currentLv>>
                Meta Terminal: Success
            <<else>> 
                Meta Terminal: Failure
            <<endif>>
            <<jump TerminalGeneralDirectory>>
-> Contamination
    <<set $currentLv = get_current_contamination_upgrade_level()>>
    Meta Terminal: Are you sure?
        -> Yes
            Meta Terminal: Making contamination upgrade now.
            <<trigger_stat_upgrade 2>>
            <<wait 2>>
            <<set $newLv = get_current_contamination_upgrade_level()>>
            <<if $newLv > $currentLv>>
                Meta Terminal: Success
            <<else>> 
                Meta Terminal: Failure
            <<endif>>
            <<jump TerminalGeneralDirectory>>
-> I want more information on each option.
