    Meta Terminal: Stamina is your capacity to fight and use manual tools.
    Meta Terminal: Contamination is your capacity to use your new abilities as a human-alien hybrid. 
    Meta Terminal: Increasing Contamination will make you able to use your abilities more times before needing replenhishment.
